Summary: 		Web Based LDAP Administration Program 
Name:			gosa
Version: 		2.6.8
Release:		1
License: 		GPL
Source: 		ftp://oss.GONICUS.de/pub/gosa/%{sourcename}.tar.bz2
URL: 			https://oss.GONICUS.de/labs/gosa/
